tics/corey-lewandowski-new-hampshire-senate-run/index.html |website=CNN |accessdate=December 31, 2019 |date=December 31, 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Chris Sununu]], incumbent [[Governor of New Hampshire]] ([[2020 New Hampshire gubernatorial election|running for re-election]])<ref>{{cite tweet|last=DiStaso|first=John|user=jdistaso|number=1128433930376445952|title=BREAKING: .@GovChrisSununu announces he's seeking a third term as #nhgov - #nhpolitics #WMUR|date=May 14, 2019|accessdate=May 14, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Endorsements===\n{{Endorsements box\n|title=Don Bolduc\n|list=\n;Individuals\n* [[Joseph Kenney]], former Executive Councilor and State Senator<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wmur.com/article/nh-primary-source-former-executive-councilor-joe-kenney-endorses-bolduc-for-us-senate/28500345|title=NH Primary Source: Former Executive Councilor Joe Kenney endorses Bolduc for US Senate|work=WMUR Manchester|last=DiStaso|first=John|date=July 25, 2019|accessdate=July 31, 2019}}</ref>\n\n* [[Tom Cotton]], United States Senator from Arkansas <ref>{{https://www.wmur.com/article/nh-primary-source-nh-republican-bolduc-endorsed-in-us-senate-run-by-sen-tom-cotton-of-arkansas/30677635}}</ref>\n\n;Organizations\n* [[Combat Veterans for Congress]]<ref>https://www.combatveteransforcongress.org/cand/3495</ref>\n* [[Senate Conservatives Fund]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.senateconservatives.com/post/3949/endorsement-general-don-bolduc|title=Support General Don Bolduc|work=[[Senate Conservatives Fund]]|date=July 25, 2019|accessdate=July 31, 2019}}</ref>\n}}\n\n{{Endorsements box\n|title=Corky Messner\n|list=\n;Individuals\n* [[William L. O'Brien|Bill O'Brien]], former Speaker of the New Hampshire House of Representatives and former 2020 New Hampshire Senate candidate<ref>https://www.wmur.com/article/bill-obrien-ends-us-senate-campaign-endorses-fellow-republican-corky-messner/32019445</ref>\n}}\n\n{{Endorsements box\n|title=Bill O'Brien (withdrawn)\n|list=\n;U.S. Senators\n* [[Ted Cruz]], [[Unite